127
00:06:18,380 --> 00:06:18,860
Yeah,

128
00:06:19,620 --> 00:06:21,020
I guess we'll just have to go
by ourselves.

129
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:23,220
Here in Lingfeng Street,

130
00:06:24,020 --> 00:06:25,180
whenever I think

131
00:06:25,180 --> 00:06:26,420
