143
00:06:58,460 --> 00:06:58,900
Come.

144
00:07:00,140 --> 00:07:00,860
I'll take you there.

145
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:13,700
Fengzha.

146
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:16,780
This thing

147
00:07:17,660 --> 00:07:18,820
