and go down the mountain.

150
00:07:24,460 --> 00:07:26,140
Getting in this
is like mounting a horse.

151
00:07:27,620 --> 00:07:28,940
In a moment, when I press the pedal,

152
00:07:29,220 --> 00:07:30,260
