174
00:09:16,980 --> 00:09:17,820
Cosplay?

175
00:09:23,980 --> 00:09:24,580
Hey there,

176
00:09:24,580 --> 00:09:25,180
your outfit

177
00:09:25,220 --> 00:09:26,220
is unique.

178
00:09:26,260 --> 00:09:26,780
Mind telling me

179
00:09:26,820 --> 00:09:27,340
which series

