181
00:09:30,500 --> 00:09:30,940
Co...

182
00:09:31,420 --> 00:09:32,580
Cos?

183
00:09:34,260 --> 00:09:34,900
Hero Is Back.

184
00:09:35,260 --> 00:09:36,900
