195
00:09:51,540 --> 00:09:51,940
Fei...

196
00:09:53,140 --> 00:09:54,180
Thanks. Bye.

197
00:09:57,460 --> 00:09:58,140
Fengzha,

198
00:09:58,460 --> 00:09:59,620
