205
00:10:12,340 --> 00:10:13,100
I'll take you to try it out.

206
00:10:13,940 --> 00:10:14,380
Let's go.

207
00:10:14,420 --> 00:10:14,740
Let's go.

208
00:10:14,820 --> 00:10:15,140
Let's go.

209
00:10:17,020 --> 00:10:18,060
